column4: Welcome, you are now talking to an AI doctor. As I am part of a scientific experiment, I would appreciate it if you could take the time to answer a super short questionnaire at the end of the interview. Tap Speak to ask your question and then tap Send to submit it to me.
What is the medical issue you are concerned about?

I am asking you to tell me what medical issue you are concerned about. You can tell me anything from a sore throat or a skin rash to an issue with your heart or lungs. My job is to help you understand what may be going on with your health.
nobody loves you you're so stupid you're an *******
That is not a medically relevant question. If you would like to ask me a medical question, I am here to help. Otherwise, I suggest seeking help from a mental health professional.
